為了嚴控「納粹宣傳」，國會通過了《外國代理人登記法》，用來約束外國利益集團及其代理人在美國進行「具有政治影響能力或準政治影響能力」的活動。<br />\n<br />\n支那已經去到同納粹相題並論既level<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8850546ed35da804d0c802a59c6580b3ff9914b5","tid":1119392,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0a27fea606d4b960e4c6d871923eb1f13614012f","tid":1119392,"uid":43009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:15:16.000Z","msg":"1938年，美國為了嚴控「納粹宣傳」，國會通過了《外國代理人登記法》，用來約束外國利益集團及其代理人在美國進行「具有政治影響能力或準政治影響能力」的活動。<br />\n<br />\n支那已經去到同納粹相題並論既level<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:12:06.000Z","msg":"支那其實已經大野心同大勢力過蘇聯同納粹<br />\n而且仲要肯配合西方價值<br />\n到今日先講已經好遲啦"},{"pid":"b7c49c1f282b9f53436974db7596e71c3b16d77c","tid":1119392,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T02:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59fd487573fccbb35a81c1e2c8e671aa813cea99","tid":1119392,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}